<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,593,151,178]" pageId="33" pageNumber="334">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,449,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="334">Artitropa erinnys nyasae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Riley" box="[456,593,152,178]" firstAuthor="Riley" pageId="33" pageNumber="334" pagination="281" refId="ref32184" refString="Riley, N. D. (1925) A revision of the continental African species of the genus Artitropa (Lep. Hesperiidae). Transactions of the Entomological Society of London, 1925, 281 - 288, plate 35. http: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1925. tb 02864. x" type="journal article" year="1925">
